title: A photochromic trinuclear dysprosium(III) single-molecule magnet with two distinct relaxation processes
content:

The photochromic trinuclear Dy(III) single-molecule magnet shows two distinct magnetic relaxation processes associated with two different Dy(III) geometry types.
